{"tid":1950004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支共又出假新聞：《自然》論文：海鮮巿場唔係源頭 官方共媒曲解：武漢唔係源頭","createTime":"2020-03-30T05:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T05:31:44.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f4261b7318ca41fff6446920be8f4f03b4afedea","tid":1950004,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CYY7X8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCYY7X8a.jpg&h=6591613a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8FFFyGx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8FFFyGx.jpg&h=fee02b29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n段英文係話海鮮巿場唔係最早<br />\n成篇冇講過武漢成個省唔係源頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n執導原文<br />\n<a href=\"https://abcnews.go.com/US/conspiracy-theorists-study-concludes-covid-19-laboratory-construct/story?id=69827832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FUS%2Fconspiracy-theorists-study-concludes-covid-19-laboratory-construct%2Fstory%3Fid%3D69827832&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2XWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=d4581a6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://abcnews.go.com/US/conspiracy-theorists-study-concludes-covid-19-laboratory-construct/story?id=69827832</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n論文原文有提過兩個源頭假說<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其中一個係武漢巿場附近既動物</span></span></strong><br />\n（ABC篇報導都有啲可疑，相當誤導）<br />\n<br />\n Instead, we propose two scenarios that can plausibly explain the origin of SARS-CoV-2: (i) natural selection in an animal host before zoonotic transfer; and (ii) natural selection in humans following zoonotic transfer. We also discuss whether selection during passage could have given rise to SARS-CoV-2.<br />\n<br />\n1. Natural selection in an animal host before zoonotic transfer<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\nAs many early cases of COVID-19 were linked to the Huanan market in Wuhan1,2, it is possible that an animal source was present at this location. </span></span></strong>Given the similarity of SARS-CoV-2 to bat SARS-CoV-like coronaviruses2, it is likely that bats serve as reservoir hosts for its progenitor. Although RaTG13, sampled from a Rhinolophus affinis bat1, is ~96% identical overall to SARS-CoV-2, its spike diverges in the RBD, which suggests that it may not bind efficiently to human ACE27 (Fig. 1a).<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41591-020-0820-9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41591-020-0820-9&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2XWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=00fc570a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41591-020-0820-9</a>"},{"pid":"a1a822be9f04e94ee7f49ff8f5bc45981100af6e","tid":1950004,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:07:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8352e3a76ab8b039d42f6b6de36710424672b4ff","tid":1950004,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:09:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老母中國共產黨<br />\n<br />\n整個民族必須殲滅"},{"pid":"68565c41b322a0f82d65208dbb2ad5beb62eb299","tid":1950004,"uid":203783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:25:47.000Z","msg":"支共又斷章取義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a82bf1c2603a96e0a192a970ba233a287a35d2","tid":1950004,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68565c41b322a0f82d65208dbb2ad5beb62eb299","tid":1950004,"uid":203783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:25:47.000Z","msg":"支共又斷章取義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:26:47.000Z","msg":"你啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7c2ba3fcb8fa4052fbe02c6d5e1d284c3e8f0b","tid":1950004,"uid":117679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:29:07.000Z","msg":"源頭係唔係武漢實驗室?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4556250807c8d064102384434b4d1630e9582982","tid":1950004,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c7c2ba3fcb8fa4052fbe02c6d5e1d284c3e8f0b","tid":1950004,"uid":117679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:29:07.000Z","msg":"源頭係唔係武漢實驗室?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:29:38.000Z","msg":"篇文否定咗哩點"},{"pid":"a4f5f23f095041eb24af4729bedb52f8621adef7","tid":1950004,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:31:44.000Z","msg":"chinese logic: 海鮮巿場 belongs to 武漢, 武漢belongs to支那, 唔係源於海鮮巿場, 所以唔係源於支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩logic黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}